OL,3,CIreland could change immigration rules
OL,4,Camid open border concerns
OL,6,FThe Irish Government says it may have
OL,7,Fto look at it's own 'immigration laws'
OL,8,Fafter The Home secretary in
OL,9,FWestminster announced sweeping reforms
OL,10,Ffor the UK.
OL,12,FShabana Mahmood unveiled the plans in
OL,13,Fthe Commons last night, after
OL,14,Fdescribing the current asylum system
OL,15,Fas " out of control and unfair."
OL,17,FThe open border between Northern
OL,18,FIreland and the Republic has raised
OL,19,Fconcerns that migrants may use
OL,20,FNorthern Ireland as a backdoor into
OL,21,Fthe south.
