OL,3,CIreland could change immigration rules
OL,4,Camid open border concerns
OL,6,FConcerns have been raised by the Irish
OL,7,FGovernment that the open border with
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland could see it become a
OL,9,Fback door for increased illegal
OL,10,Fimmigration into the South, and it
OL,11,Fisn't ruling out updating its own
OL,12,Fmeasures in response.
OL,14,FJim O'Callaghan Minister for Justice
OL,15,FIreland said: "Changes to the UK
OL,16,Fasylum laws can have an impact in
OL,17,FIreland and have had an impact in the
OL,18,Fpast.
