OL,6,F"What it does indicate is that I
OL,7,Fsuppose we need to be nimble in
OL,8,FIreland as we may need to change our
OL,9,Flaws and our provisions as well to
OL,10,Frespond to any changes that have taken
OL,11,Fplace in the UK."
OL,13,FIn June, racially motivated violence
OL,14,Ferupted in Ballymena and spread to
OL,15,Fother parts of the country, and anti-
OL,16,Fimmigration protests have turned
OL,17,Fviolent in the South too.
OL,19,FMigrants living here say Westminster's
OL,20,Fnew proposals only help to stoke the
OL,21,Fflames of division.
