OL,4,Camid open border concerns
OL,6,FSuleima Abdulahi from Horn of Africa
OL,7,FPeople's Aid NI said: "It's very
OL,8,Funfair. I think the crisis we have, it
OL,9,Fis not responsibility of refugees and
OL,10,Fasylum seekers.
OL,12,F"We're just scapegoating them. We know
OL,13,Falready that that has made an impact
OL,14,Fin in terms of rhetoric and
OL,15,Fmisinformation for the public and it's
OL,16,Fnot a public interest to divide us."
OL,18,FHowever, the reforms do have the
OL,19,Fsupport of some in Stormont.
