OL,3,CIreland could change immigration rules
OL,4,Camid open border concerns
OL,6,FDUP MLA Johnathan Buckley said: "I
OL,7,Fthink it's a recognition of the huge
OL,8,Fissues that illegal immigration
OL,9,Fcontinues to pretend. I welcome that
OL,10,Fshe is now proposing to bring forward
OL,11,Flegislation.
OL,13,F"We will now look at the detail of
OL,14,Fthat legislation and ensure that it's
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland is included within
OL,16,Fits provisions, that we can have a
OL,17,Frobust border policy that protects our
OL,18,Fcitizens and controls our borders."
